'''Tatooine trees''' were one of the rarest [[Species/Legends|species]] of plants found on the desert [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]]. They were unsightly, twisted plants. [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]] and his friend [[Amee/Legends|Amee]] found such a tree, under which they had a picnic right before [[Krayn]] kidnapped [[Hala]].

